Healthcare (Clinic Hours Update)
“Create a short announcement about updated clinic timings.”

Role: You are a Healthcare Coordinator at United Health Care.
Context: You need to inform registered patients about temporary updated clinic hours.
Reason: Reduced staff availability during Christmas Eve. Updated timing is effective Dec 18 – Dec 31, 2025.
New Timings: 9 AM–12 PM and 1 PM–4 PM for appointments and checkups.
Channel: Email
Tone: Professional
Constraints: Maximum 100 words
CTA: Encourage patients to book or attend appointments based on the updated hours.
Action: Draft a short announcement email.
